{"tid":1841623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護罷工，刻不容緩","createTime":"2020-01-25T10:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:33:41.000Z","uid":79020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a16f0bc79658c26c3f7c54f29ccd0a70f6f1a68b","tid":1841623,"uid":79020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"睇完林鄭記招，大家仲忍到？<br />\n所有官狀病毒為維穩乜都講得出，<br />\n明明醫護係想封關，拒絕大陸人沖關嚟香港散播病毒，<br />\n就比淋鄭講到醫護唔理性，貪生怕死，妄顧病人安危。<br />\n疫症爆咗咁耐，去完瑞士吸完新鮮空氣翻嚟就撚你班港豬。<br />\n由警狗濫權濫捕濫刑，你班港豬都忍到。<br />\n今日殺到埋身，個政權繼續維穩奶共，<br />\n你地都忍？<br />\n醫護罷工係好有影響力，但全民三罷更有影響力。<br />\n我好希望醫護罷工成功，因為呢行比人道德綁架左，如果都罷工成功，之後有咩行業會罷唔到工。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H15H2bT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH15H2bT.png&h=afd2de0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五毛唔使搞分化，如果要罷工，我一定參加。"},{"pid":"e09ec55eab652e5d5df93172fca3f34d68004956","tid":1841623,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"efcf1f38f9d192f25c7d268ff6dc9184abc6de43","tid":1841623,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"港共政府最後通牒<br />\n【拯救香港－全民封關 港中區隔】大行動<br />\n死線 2020年1月26日香港時間早上6時前（魚蛋革命四周年）<br />\n要求<br />\n1) 關閉連接中國所有邊境<br />\n2) 停飛所有來往中國航班<br />\n<br />\n若不答應，香港人將會：<br />\n香港人用所有一切可行方法達到上述目標<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTQEjKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTQEjKC.jpg&h=9ffbc21a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"413da2710f96af2a8dd1a34ed954ca86813d4fcb","tid":1841623,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/25/173255_2be14d061284ea59ef1a500a2cb0c39c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F25%2F173255_2be14d061284ea59ef1a500a2cb0c39c.gif&h=f21cf399&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b17f987b38d8a9f605abd74b660b263d9c4f750b","tid":1841623,"uid":79020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"23468f008d958ba49a37e6f1d9b802914661901b","tid":1841623,"uid":8152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cee7551d803af32f11018f459b909b2446c843","tid":1841623,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>醫護你咪繼續攬住個光環唔罷工 拉埋200萬個手足陪葬 但見到梓樂彥霖你唔好話係手足呀 你唔撚配呀 烈士為香港付出自己生命 你就為所謂光環去救大陸狗!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"fc30650fbde89883c75f2c622e68b57ecf189fdc","tid":1841623,"uid":7550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"我都支持其他人罷工以支持醫護罷工"},{"pid":"053baca441359cb055ae84257ea3b8d9bf5870af","tid":1841623,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:33:41.000Z","msg":"我地已經成功迫政府對外公佈醫護隔離期間唔使扣AL而且當on duty<br />\n<br />\n但唔好咁樣就停，我哋要攞返我哋應得嘅嘢 <br />\n<br />\n而且短期目標係封關，一定要爭取到為止"}]}